<p>Due to a broadband outage, John and Dave go low(er) tech this week, at least in terms of the recording methods. That said, the show is still a geek gab, and is anything but low tech! John and Dave talk about their favorite hardware and Dave even gets a great rant about cell phones.</p>
<p><strong>Show notes for TMO To Go: Mac Geek Gab For August 15th, 2005</strong></p>
<p>Podcast Link: <a href="http://mp3.macobserver.com/podcast/mgg11.mp3" data-wpel-link="external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">TMO To Go: Mac Geek Gab, August 15th, 2005</a></p>
<p>Due to a broadband outage, John and Dave go low(er) tech this week, at least in terms of the recording methods. That said, the show is still a geek gab, and is anything but low tech! John and Dave talk about their favorite hardware and Dave even gets a great rant about cell phones.</p>
